	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really doubt there's any actual processor speed change here, as the CPU has a fixed clock and there is no way to change that in software. It's much more likely that this is just a bug, as Memblers said. I don't think it's due to pooling $2002 though, since missing VBlanks would actually make the game slower... We'd have to take a look at that part of the game while it's running to have a better idea, though. But that game does not seem very fun, as the angry Nintendo nerd advised. =D

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


